<br>
I am not sure what else I can say...I think that's a good solution as it is getting hard for us to control SOME peoples signatures, as they just never follow the rules. We can't be losing users because of these rules, so it's probably best if FFA, the busiest forum, no longer allows sigs. People have access to users profiles, and they generally will have a link. If they don't have a link it's probably a spammer anyhow, so it should be fine. It's not hard, and to be honest, I don't think I will miss signatures in here...<br>
<br>
We can't really put restrictions anymore on the size of the image, or the amount of code, as it's too much work and people will always argue where their signature fits in... <p></p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1>   &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbbardenfrm31.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1867.topic&index=22><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/reply.gif border=0 width=20 height=20 alt="reply to this message" align=absmiddle></a>   <br><br></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#200985><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub103.ezboard.com/usudsybubblebath.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sudsy Bubblebath</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.geocities.com/candijdixon/Ezboard/bananapic.gif " BORDER=0> </span><br><BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/candijdixon/Ezboard/redcup.gif height=64 width=64><br> <span class=usertitle>Melting<br /><img src=http://www.bbarden.com/img/levels/userlevel-2-2.gif /></span><br>  ezSupporter<br> Posts: <b>121</b><br></td><td valign=top align=left class=m width=80%><span class=m><font color=#99CCFF>Posted: 9/3/02 12:11:51 am</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br><span class=title> <img src="http://www.bbarden.com/img/em/biggrinking.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: One sig per topic rule</span><hr size=1> I think you should turn the sigs. off in the Free For All forum and do just what you said, Ben <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.bbarden.com/img/em/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   It sounds like a great idea ... and promotion ... hehe, so what?  I used to be the queen of promotion <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.bbarden.com/img/em/wink.gif